enter; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 433.3;"></span><span data-cds="Icon" class="absolute inset-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 433.3;"></span></span></span></button><div class="flex items-center"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="[content-visibility:auto] [contain-intrinsic-size:auto_400px] px-2 -mx-2 pb-8 -mb-8 print:[content-visibility:visible]"><div data-test-render-count="2"><div class="group" style="height: auto; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="contents"><div data-is-streaming="false" class="group relative relative pb-3" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><h2 data-find-omitted="" class="sr-only select-none" data-aria-hidden="true" aria-hidden="true">Claude ha respondido: Perfecto, ya tengo todos tus datos.</h2><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div data-find-omitted="" class="contents"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2" data-aria-hidden="true" aria-hidden="true"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate font-base">Visualizó un archivo, ejecutó un comando</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Visualizó un archivo, ejecutó un comando</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;" data-aria-hidden="true" aria-hidden="true"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0" data-aria-hidden="true" aria-hidden="true"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Perfecto, ya tengo todos tus datos. Encontré tu fila en el Excel:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Nombre:</strong> Vidal Vidal Benjamin Jose</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Código:</strong> 001V-21</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Empresa:</strong> Integración Digital SA</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Hostname:</strong> RTR-INTDIG</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>IP Loopback:</strong> 10.1.21.1 / 255.255.255.0</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Desc. WAN:</strong> Enlace-WAN-Tocopilla</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Banner:</strong> ACCESO RESTRINGIDO - INTDIG</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>NTP:</strong> 1.1.1.1</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Noto que el archivo <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.docx</code> que tienes tiene algunos valores del template de ejemplo (como <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">DataCenter Sur Ltda</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">8.8.8.8</code>, etc.) que <strong>no corresponden a tus datos</strong>. Hay que corregir eso.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Vamos a construir todo paso a paso. Empecemos con lo primero: generar todos los archivos del proyecto. ¿Estás trabajando directamente en la VM DEVASC (y necesitas los scripts listos para copiar/ejecutar ahí), o quieres que te genere los archivos aquí para revisarlos primero?</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Lo que vamos a hacer es:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Crear <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">vars/vars_001V-21.yaml</code> con tus datos correctos</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Generar el <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">testbed_001V-21.yaml</code> para Fase 1</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Generar el <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">playbook_001V-21.yaml</code> para Fase 2</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Generar <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">validacion_netconf.py</code> para Fase 3</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Generar <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">validacion_restconf.py</code> para Fase 4</li>
