an class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">3</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">192.168</span><span>.56.101</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Paso 2 — Verificar que SSH responde</h4>
