<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Este comando va a tomar un par de minutos. Vas a ver cada tarea con su estado (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">changed</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">ok</code>, etc.).</p>
